# dev-env — Cursor Rules

> Auto-loaded by Cursor IDE when working in this repository.
> These rules mirror `copilot-instructions.md` (authoritative source).

---

## Safety — NEVER auto-install

- No package manager commands (`winget`, `npm`, `apt`, `brew`, `scoop`, `choco`) without explicit user confirmation
- `safeMode` profiles (work, server) block all installs unless explicitly confirmed
- Phase 00 and 00-fallback detect prerequisites — they NEVER install
- Phase 30 clone is always read-only

## PowerShell Conventions

- Shebang: `#!/usr/bin/env pwsh`
- Header block with ROLE, RUN, INPUT, OUTPUT
- `[CmdletBinding(SupportsShouldProcess)]` for mutation scripts
- Full cmdlet names — NO aliases (`ls`, `gc`, `%`, `?`, `select`, `sort`, `where`)
- `Join-Path` for paths — no string concatenation
- `Write-Host` for user output, `Write-Output` for pipeline data
- Bilingual comments: English functional, Czech context
- Emoji indicators: ✅ OK, ❌ FAIL, ⚠️ WARN
- Phase header: `Write-Host ">>> PHASE XX — NAME" -ForegroundColor <color>`

## Pipeline Order

```
00 → 30 → 10 → 20 → 40 → 50 → 60 → 70
```

## JSON Profiles

- Inherit from `base.json` via `"extends": "base"`
- Required keys: `extends`, `identity`, `proxy`, `safeMode`
- Secrets canonical source: `profiles/base.json#/secrets`

## Secrets — NEVER commit

`~/.ssh/`, `machines.json`, `~/.dev-env/config/`, `~/.gitconfig.user`, `~/.npmrc`, `~/.aws/`, `~/.azure/`

## Documentation Style

- Markdown with bilingual headers: `# 🏗️ English / Česky`
- Emoji section prefixes
- Mermaid diagrams for flows
- Tables for structured data

## Key Files

- `manifest.json` — Authoritative metadata and file listing
- `ai/context.md` — Full AI lifecycle and decision tree
- `.github/instructions/` — Language-specific conventions
